<p data-start=\"474\" data-end=\"606\"><strong data-start=\"474\" data-end=\"498\">Personal Information<\/strong>: Your name, email address, payment details, and any other data provided during registration or purchases.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"607\" data-end=\"716\"><p data-start=\"609\" data-end=\"716\"><strong data-start=\"609\" data-end=\"623\">Usage Data<\/strong>: Details such as your IP address, browser type, pages visited, and time spent on the site.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"717\" data-end=\"835\"><p data-start=\"719\" data-end=\"835\"><strong data-start=\"719\" data-end=\"730\">Cookies<\/strong>: Small data files stored on your device to improve your browsing experience (see Section 6 for details).<\/p><\/li><\/ul><h3 data-start=\"837\" data-end=\"872\">\u00a0<\/h3><h3 data-start=\"837\" data-end=\"872\">3. How We Use Your Information<\/h3><p data-start=\"873\" data-end=\"922\">Your data may be used for the following purposes:<\/p><ul data-start=\"924\" data-end=\"1247\"><li data-start=\"924\" data-end=\"975\"><p data-start=\"926\" data-end=\"975\">To deliver and improve our courses and services<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"976\" data-end=\"1027\"><p data-start=\"978\" data-end=\"1027\">To process transactions and manage your account<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"1028\" data-end=\"1113\"><p data-start=\"1030\" data-end=\"1113\">To send newsletters, course updates, and promotional emails (with opt-out option)<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"1114\" data-end=\"1173\"><p data-start=\"1116\" data-end=\"1173\">To monitor site performance and enhance user experience<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"1174\" data-end=\"1247\"><p data-start=\"1176\" data-end=\"1247\">To enforce our Terms and Conditions and comply with legal obligations<\/p><\/li><\/ul><h3 data-start=\"1249\" data-end=\"1281\">\u00a0<\/h3><h3 data-start=\"1249\" data-end=\"1281\">4. How We Protect Your Data<\/h3><p data-start=\"1282\" data-end=\"1368\">We take your data security seriously. We employ industry-standard measures, including:<\/p><ul data-start=\"1370\" data-end=\"1528\"><li data-start=\"1370\" data-end=\"1420\"><p data-start=\"1372\" data-end=\"1420\">Secure, encrypted servers and payment gateways<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"1421\" data-end=\"1460\"><p data-start=\"1423\" data-end=\"1460\">Regular security checks and updates<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"1461\" data-end=\"1528\"><p data-start=\"1463\" data-end=\"1528\">Controlled access to personal data by authorized personnel only<\/p><\/li><\/ul><h3 data-start=\"1530\" data-end=\"1562\">\u00a0<\/h3><h3 data-start=\"1530\" data-end=\"1562\">5. Sharing Your Information<\/h3><p data-start=\"1563\" data-end=\"1644\">We do <strong data-start=\"1569\" data-end=\"1576\">not<\/strong> sell, rent, or trade your personal data. We may share it only with:<\/p><ul data-start=\"1646\" data-end=\"1825\"><li data-start=\"1646\" data-end=\"1704\"><p data-start=\"1648\" data-end=\"1704\"><strong data-start=\"1648\" data-end=\"1678\">Trusted payment processors<\/strong> for secure transactions<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"1705\" data-end=\"1777\"><p data-start=\"1707\" data-end=\"1777\"><strong data-start=\"1707\" data-end=\"1728\">Service providers<\/strong> who assist in site management and improvements<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"1778\" data-end=\"1825\"><p data-start=\"1780\" data-end=\"1825\"><strong data-start=\"1780\" data-end=\"1801\">Legal authorities<\/strong>, when required by law<\/p><\/li><\/ul><h3 data-start=\"1827\" data-end=\"1868\">\u00a0<\/h3><h3 data-start=\"1827\" data-end=\"1868\">6. Cookies and Tracking Technologies<\/h3><p data-start=\"1869\" data-end=\"1951\">Cookies help us personalize your experience and analyze traffic. They allow us to:<\/p><ul data-start=\"1953\" data-end=\"2037\"><li data-start=\"1953\" data-end=\"1982\"><p data-start=\"1955\" data-end=\"1982\">Remember your preferences<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"1983\" data-end=\"2008\"><p data-start=\"1985\" data-end=\"2008\">Measure website usage<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"2009\" data-end=\"2037\"><p data-start=\"2011\" data-end=\"2037\">Deliver relevant content<\/p><\/li><\/ul><p data-start=\"2039\" data-end=\"2093\">You can control cookies through your browser settings.<\/p><p data-start=\"2039\" data-end=\"2093\">\u00a0<\/p><h3 data-start=\"2095\" data-end=\"2114\">7. Your Rights<\/h3><p data-start=\"2115\" data-end=\"2137\">You have the right to:<\/p><ul data-start=\"2139\" data-end=\"2316\"><li data-start=\"2139\" data-end=\"2168\"><p data-start=\"2141\" data-end=\"2168\">Access your personal data<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"2169\" data-end=\"2211\"><p data-start=\"2171\" data-end=\"2211\">Request corrections to inaccurate data<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"2212\" data-end=\"2284\"><p data-start=\"2214\" data-end=\"2284\">Request deletion of your information (subject to legal requirements)<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"2285\" data-end=\"2316\"><p data-start=\"2287\" data-end=\"2316\">Opt-out of marketing emails<\/p><\/li><\/ul><p data-start=\"2318\" data-end=\"2381\">To exercise these rights, please contact us at the email below.<\/p><p data-start=\"2318\" data-end=\"2381\">\u00a0<\/p><h3 data-start=\"2383\" data-end=\"2421\">8. Changes to This Privacy Policy<\/h3><p data-start=\"2422\" data-end=\"2591\">We may revise this policy from time to time. All changes will be reflected on this page with a revised update date. Please check this page periodically to stay informed.<\/p><p data-start=\"2422\" data-end=\"2591\">\u00a0<\/p><h3 data-start=\"2593\" data-end=\"2611\">9. Contact Us<\/h3><p data-start=\"2612\" data-end=\"2659\">Have questions or concerns? We\u2019re here to help.<\/p><p data-start=\"2661\" data-end=\"2736\">\ud83d\udce7 <strong data-start=\"2664\" data-end=\"2674\">Email:<\/strong> <a class=\"cursor-pointer\" rel=\"noopener\" data-start=\"2675\" data-end=\"2736\">learnwitharshyan@gmail.com<\/a><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","pr